                          <DESC>
                            <L-2 L="EN">Port pin mode from mode list. NOTE: While configuring the PortPinMode, ensure that the selected mux mode is available for the specific device variant by checking the datasheet as the pinmuxmode list contains a superset of values for all the variants.</L-2>
